@node "history" "AmiGenerator - History"

 v0.33 - 010909
       - Updated to the latest Generator sources.
       - Changed the version number to the same as the official release.
       - Made a port based upon the portable consol interface.
       - Made a "Turbo" version with less features but greater speed.
       - Removed AGA support.

 v0.34 - 011021
       - Updated to the latest Generator sources.
       - Added many options: NOSOUND, NOZ80, NOFM, NOPSG, LACE, LATENCY,
         FRAGMENTS, FREQ, REQ. Read the usage section for further information.
       - Added AGA support to the T-version.
       - The console version now support 16bit as well.

@endnode
